{"title":"Quirk Cycles TITAN Custom Titanium Road Bike","link":"https://theradavist.com/quirk-cycles-titan-custom-titanium-road-bike/","date":1714576383000,"content":"<p>The <a href=\"https://www.quirkcycles.com/titan\" target=\"_blank\">TITAN</a> is the first custom titanium bicycle offering from <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/quirk-cycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Quirk Cycles</a>. Known for their elegant and excellently crafted steel bikes, the new titanium TITAN expands Quirk’s catalog with Columbus Hyperion tubing for a “fast, responsive and beautifully compliant ride.”</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1667\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_12.jpg?fit=1200,1667&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_12.jpg?w=2500&amp;quality=75 2500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_12.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_12.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_12.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_12.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_12.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>For a decade, Quirk Cycles has been refining what a modern steel road bike should be, using innovative manufacturing techniques. Now, they have applied their knowledge to the matchless ride feel of titanium.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1667\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_06.jpg?fit=1200,1667&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_06.jpg?w=2500&amp;quality=75 2500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_06.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_06.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_06.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_06.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_06.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>The TITAN is their first titanium road bike. It claims to be fast, responsive and beautifully compliant. It’s a contemporary design engineered in advanced materials, “the ultimate modern road bike.”</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1667\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_13.jpg?fit=1200,1667&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_13.jpg?w=2500&amp;quality=75 2500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_13.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_13.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_13.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_13.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_13.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1667\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_17.jpg?fit=1200,1667&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_17.jpg?w=2500&amp;quality=75 2500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_17.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_17.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_17.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_17.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_17.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Quirk Cycles is dedicated to pushing the boundaries of bike production by harnessing the potential of the latest materials and technology. While they honor tradition, they are driven by a relentless pursuit of innovation, constantly seeking fresh and inventive approaches.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1667\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_07.jpg?fit=1200,1667&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_07.jpg?w=2500&amp;quality=75 2500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_07.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_07.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_07.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_07.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Quirk_Cycles_TITAN_07.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<h3>Specs</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Columbus Hyperion titanium tubing</li>\n<li>Progressive tube diameters (proportionally sized tubes for ultimate compliance to stiffness ratio)</li>\n<li>Titanium Fork</li>\n<li>Integrated cabling (in-house 3D headtube offers fully hidden cables routed in frame)</li>\n<li>Disc brake equipped</li>\n<li>3D printed titanium construction</li>\n<li>35mm max tire size</li>\n<li>T47 BB standard</li>\n<li>27.2mm seatpost</li>\n<li>160mm max rotor</li>\n<li>Frameset: £6500 inc VAT / Full builds starting at £9.5k</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.quirkcycles.com/titan\" target=\"_blank\">Quirk Cycles</a></p>\n<p><em>Photos courtesy of <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/thisisnikoo/\" target=\"_blank\">Nikoo Hamzavi</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/quirk-cycles-titan-custom-titanium-road-bike/\">Quirk Cycles TITAN Custom Titanium Road Bike</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"Josh Weinberg","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"99912c6b21db5f4dfaa29cd6bbae80bb2d14cc83ddbe8dde1772807941437c70","category":"Cycling"}